
# Blog CRUD Application
This is a simple blog CRUD application built using PHP and MySQL. It follows the MVC (Model-View-Controller) architecture pattern.
# Project Structure
project/
├── config/ # Database config
│ └── database.php
├── models # Database config
│ └──post_model.php
│
├── controllers/ # Controller classes
│ └── Post.php
├── models/ # Model classes
│ ├── User.php
│ └── post_models.php
│
├── views/ # View files (HTML/PHP)
│ ├── post/ ->create.php,edit.php
│ ├── partials/alert.php
│ ├── index.php
│ └── layouts/ ->header.php,footer.php
│
└── index.php # Entry point


echo "<pre>";
print_r($posts);
echo "</pre>";



Posts:
post_id pk
user_id fk
title 
body
date
; created_id
; updated_id

Users:
user_id pk
name
email
phone
password
; created_at
; updated_at

Comments:
comment_id pk
post_id fk
user_id fk
user_email
comment_date
comment_text

PostToComments:
post_id pk
category_id pk

Categories:
category_id pk
